---
<section class="manifesto" id="manifesto">
  <div class="manifesto-inner">
    <div class="manifesto-mark">&ldquo;</div>
    <div class="manifesto-eyebrow">Why we built this</div>
    <div class="manifesto-body">
      <p>
        For centuries, people have wanted to be in <em>more than one place at once.</em>
        The bottleneck of every job that depends on understanding people has always been the same:
        <strong>one person, in one chair, having one conversation at a time.</strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        AnyInterview is what you get when that stops being true.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="manifesto-signature">
      <span class="names">Amdal &amp; Weston</span> · co-founders
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section.manifesto {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: clamp(100px, 16vh, 180px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 56px);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  section.manifesto::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% 30%, rgba(29,53,87,0.06), transparent 60%);
  }

  .manifesto-inner {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .manifesto-mark {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 60px;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .manifesto-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .manifesto-eyebrow::before, .manifesto-eyebrow::after {
    content: "";
    width: 22px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--rule);
  }

  .manifesto-body {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(20px, 2.2vw, 28px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .manifesto-body p {
    margin-bottom: 1.4em;
  }
  .manifesto-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .manifesto-body em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .manifesto-body strong {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .manifesto-signature {
    margin-top: 48px;
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .manifesto-signature .names {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.005em;
  }
</style>
